    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aspect is an early access retro-inspired roguelite dungeon crawler, where enemies drop Aspects - fragments of their power, that you can use against them. With a variety of enemies to face, weapons to find, and procedurally generated levels, no two playthroughs are the same</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The current Early Access version has: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ weapons, with unique mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A diverse cast of enemies, each one a unique challenge - but if you can get their Aspects, you can turn the tides and use these powers against them!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two different types of cave to explore, each one offering different loot and monsters. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aspects: Accessories, gained from each enemy, that let the player use some of the enemy's power. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All kinds of structures to be encountered in the caves and offer the player new weapons and loot. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A retro-inspired pixel art design, with similarly inspired music. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The aim of the finished game is replay ability - no two playthroughs will be the same, and much more content is planned to come.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you make it through the dungeon and collect all the aspects?</p>",
